                    <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold mb-6">Our Story</h1>
                    <p class="text-lg text-[#7A7A7A] mb-4">
                        The gig economy is broken. We have seen firsthand the chaotic gig economy where freelancers (independent businesses) face unstable income and companies are exposed to legal risks. This reality is especially acute for new immigrants and non-EU citizens navigating complex Finnish compliance requirements.
                    </p>
                    <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-lg text-[#7A7A7A] space-y-2">
                        <li>The current system leads to fragmented tasks and a lack of career pathways.</li>
                        <li>Freelancers are often trapped in low-income cycles, without a clear path for professional growth.</li>
                        <li>Companies struggle with complex compliance and administrative burdens.</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p class="text-lg text-[#7A7A7A] mt-4">
                        CodFleet was founded to build a compliance-first bridge. We are a compliance + invoicing hub that provides a professional backbone for Finland's gig economy. We are here to transform tasks/opportunities into sustainable careers.
                    </p>
